  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_dental_council">General Dental Council</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_regulatory_body">Regulatory Body</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_dental_council">General Dental Council</xref>
 aims to:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>
protect 
                          <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
promote confidence in dentists and 
                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_dental_care_professional">Dental Care Professionals</xref>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>be at the forefront of healthcare regulation.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_dental_council">General Dental Council</xref>'s role is to:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>register qualified professionals</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>set standards of dental practice and conduct</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>assure the quality of dental education</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>ensure professionals keep up-to-date</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
help 
                          <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 with complaints about a dentist or a 
                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_dental_care_professional">Dental Care Professional</xref>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
strengthen 
                          <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 protection                </p>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_dental_council">General Dental Council</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_dental_council">General Dental Council</xref>
Â website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.gdc-uk.org/about/what-we-do"
               scope="external"
               format="html">What we do</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
